20:18.634 --> 20:20.260
- Wait, Miguel.
- Yeah. No, I, I--

20:20.469 --> 20:21.970
Just hang on.

20:21.970 --> 20:23.430
- Miguel, just listen to me.
- What I told you today,

20:23.430 --> 20:24.681
