22:17.294 --> 22:19.421
- like the old couple in <i>Titanic!</i>
- Oh god!

22:30.849 --> 22:34.519
Yeah, I'm gonna backtrack just a smidge.

22:36.605 --> 22:41.026
Since the dawn of time...
there's been exactly one sign.

22:42.944 --> 22:44.404
And this was it.

22:44.946 --> 22:47.491
- I'm gonna go.
-  Please wait.

22:47.491 --> 22:50.452
But the good news is, this whole thing,

22:50.452 --> 22:53.372
I'm sure this will make
a great chapter for your novel.

22:53.372 --> 22:54.664
Miguel!

23:03.340 --> 23:05.092
He is out of his mind.

23:05.092 --> 23:08.720
